snippet.title: Ode to Todd - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Version 1 available now! https://sodapop67.itch.io/an-ode-to-todd-the-toad-frogcare

Play with your frogs in the nest! Name them, give them outfits, and let them play with toys they find while exploring. Explore with your frogs in the maze! Protect them from wasps while they eat flies and look for toys.

for updates subscribe! and follow me here:
📚 sodazone.neocities.org

🎮 sodapop67.itch.io
🐤 twitter.com/Soda_POP_67
📷 instagram.com/soda_pop_games/

- graphic design, game design, and code by Calvin "SodaPOP" Plank

- trailer music by Grant Binkley (more in-game music by Carlos Najera)
